author_name": "BABYBLUE", "author_id": "3b36c7afb340fc4ac63a94a5c32541d2", "author_is_anonymous": false, "child_comment": []}, {"url_token": "san-jie-jiao-xiang-le-meng-bai-ye", "headline": "高校青椒，日语讲师喵", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "680044772", "reply_comment_id": "0", "reply_root_comment_id": "680044772", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "汽车小白➕新手女司机，我就是预算二十左右，买个上班用的小车，本来是去看Q2L的，单位里对Q2L、A4、Q5有优惠。结果到店里体验了一下Q2L后感觉不喜欢，出门要走时看到外面停着一台红色的落着尘土的小车，我一下子就喜欢了，看了一下才知道是三厢款A3，问了一下价格也很合适，虽然用不上单位的优惠了，但真的是多看两眼的车。后来去另一家店看价钱，这款小车直接摆在一入门的地方，应该就是“入门”车吧。真的很漂亮。去了两次还是很喜欢第三次讲好价钱就买啦。结果老被人喷空间小，花二十万多不如买个中型车或者再添添买个4L啥的，添添难道买个裸车不成，最起码得上个中配吧，少不了小十万。可是这是不管在用途还是预算还是我要求的条件上最适合自己的呀", "like_count": 4, "author_name": "宝贝加油加油", "author_id": "2cbb051511f06b09d27f69940d3ccd28", "author_is_anonymous": false, "child_comment": [{"url_token": "hong-tao-k-18-95", "headline": "自见者不明；自是者不彰；自伐者无功；自矜者不长。", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "680387904", "reply_comment_id": "680044772", "reply_root_comment_id": "680044772", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "没错，按自己的预算喜欢就好了。车是自己开，后排真正用到的时候也不多。买车一般都是中高配，低配的别为难自己，实际使用中肯定会觉得当时干嘛不加点预算上中配，脑子不好", "like_count": 0, "author_name": "红桃K", "author_id": "3a1853a27d43c25b61912b4cd1dbbcec", "author_is_anonymous": false}]}, {"url_token": "zhao-meng-fu-47", "headline": "社会主义接班人", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "679558134", "reply_comment_id": "0", "reply_root_comment_id": "679558134", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "可以免息就不要全款？ 作为两辆车都是全款的表示不同意", "like_count": 3, "author_name": "莱纳斯", "author_id": "b2532fef8b583ebbdda4829c136ef16a", "author_is_anonymous": false, "child_comment": [{"url_token": "weiruolanwocaonima", "headline": "", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "690907324", "reply_comment_id": "680805087", "reply_root_comment_id": "679558134", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "如果不是实在没有办法全款，千万不要贷款！否则你就进入了厂商和4S店给你设计的套里了，老铁你就不要再误导后面的兄弟了。", "like_count": 5, "author_name": "知乎用户410uo9", "author_id": "b83cff6613775b1acaad553b7c1bf758", "author_is_anonymous": false}, {"url_token": "weiruolanwocaonima", "headline": "", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "690906500", "reply_comment_id": "680805087", "reply_root_comment_id": "679558134", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "而且还不算如果做贷款他们一般会收服务费，就算你说这个服务费可以免除，他们也会要求你的保险必须全部上齐，也不会给你返保险的代理费，更不要说免息的贷款一般提前还款还要收5000左右的违约金，登记证要被扣，如果你要卖车或者抵押车根本没有办法。还有因为是贷款，必须上盗抢险甚至还要上GPS设备，一大堆冤枉钱等着你出！哪里就有便宜让你赚了？", "like_count": 3, "author_name": "知乎用户410uo9", "author_id": "b83cff6613775b1acaad553b7c1bf758", "author_is_anonymous": false}, {"url_token": "weiruolanwocaonima", "headline": "", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "690905620", "reply_comment_id": "680805087", "reply_root_comment_id": "679558134", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "不是这样的，一般来说，如果全款的话,你可以直接和4S争取到更大的优惠力度，直接在购买的时候就一步到位，如果贷款，那么优惠力度会变小，原本给你优惠2万的，可能只给你优惠1万，甚至按照指导价卖给你，如果要拿到全款的优惠，他们就不会给你做什么免息。反正横竖都是要从你身上赚回来的。你不傻，4S和厂商也不傻。", "like_count": 3, "author_name": "知乎用户410uo9", "author_id": "b83cff6613775b1acaad553b7c1bf758", "author_is_anonymous": false}, {"url_token": "xiao-lu-ding-ding-76", "headline": "", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "720659938", "reply_comment_id": "690907324", "reply_root_comment_id": "679558134", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "正解，4儿子又不傻", "like_count": 2, "author_name": "小鹿叮叮", "author_id": "b4962b666a6d2aba5f2471fb6967003a", "author_is_anonymous": false}, {"url_token": "weiruolanwocaonima", "headline": "", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "690906695", "reply_comment_id": "680805087", "reply_root_comment_id": "679558134", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "你忘了如果全款可以直接要求4S店再优惠5000...", "like_count": 1, "author_name": "知乎用户410uo9", "author_id": "b83cff6613775b1acaad553b7c1bf758", "author_is_anonymous": false}, {"url_token": "zhao-meng-fu-47", "headline": "社会主义接班人", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "680730137", "reply_comment_id": "679760966", "reply_root_comment_id": "679558134", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "然而普通人能找到多高的投资？有多少人理财方面做得到专业？", "like_count": 1, "author_name": "莱纳斯", "author_id": "b2532fef8b583ebbdda4829c136ef16a", "author_is_anonymous": false}, {"url_token": "hong-tao-k-18-95", "headline": "自见者不明；自是者不彰；自伐者无功；自矜者不长。", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "679760966", "reply_comment_id": "679558134", "reply_root_comment_id": "679558134", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "有这些钱去做点别的投资多好。只能说大佬你好，大佬再见[捂脸]", "like_count": 1, "author_name": "红桃K", "author_id": "3a1853a27d43c25b61912b4cd1dbbcec", "author_is_anonymous": false}, {"url_token": "hong-suan-zao-super", "headline": "", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "715616367", "reply_comment_id": "679558134", "reply_root_comment_id": "679558134", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "上海这边没事，跟我说贷款和全款没有两样，不收手续费，不押大本登记证啥的……从中国银行贷的", "like_count": 0, "author_name": "红酸枣super", "author_id": "899061d41a5ffed2a0c8b85bd25b708d", "author_is_anonymous": false}, {"url_token": "hong-tao-k-18-95", "headline": "自见者不明；自是者不彰；自伐者无功；自矜者不长。", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "680805087", "reply_comment_id": "680730137", "reply_root_comment_id": "679558134", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "就是不投资，免息贷款的钱握手里两年也抵抗了这两年如果全款的通货膨胀，找不到投资不会理财的，就是买货币基金两年也有大几千的收益。<br>举例，免息贷款7万，拿这7万去买收益最低的活期的货币基金，1万块一天的收益是1块，7万块两年的收益，=7×30天×12个月×2年=5040，这还是按最低的收益算的，也没加上你全款的通货膨胀的沉没成本", "like_count": 0, "author_name": "红桃K", "author_id": "3a1853a27d43c25b61912b4cd1dbbcec", "author_is_anonymous": false}]}, {"url_token": "ehangz", "headline": "", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "677086887", "reply_comment_id": "0", "reply_root_comment_id": "677086887", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "“珍惜临牌”这说法和背后的想法就不妥吧，就算是临牌也得遵照交通规则来用车啊！", "like_count": 2, "author_name": "ehangz", "author_id": "5713a8d1d9bd7f18068ef5eb9d85604b", "author_is_anonymous": false, "child_comment": [{"url_token": "ehangz", "headline": "", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "677220665", "reply_comment_id": "677088867", "reply_root_comment_id": "677086887", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "况且其他答复里面也说了 临牌也一样记分扣分的，而且一般到得扣分了，那属于 妨碍安全驾驶的行为 了(想得到的就是除了扣1分的 未按照规定放置年检标识和未随身携带驾驶证或行驶证，可能算不上 妨碍安全驾驶)。", "like_count": 1, "author_name": "ehangz", "author_id": "5713a8d1d9bd7f18068ef5eb9d85604b", "author_is_anonymous": false}, {"url_token": "ehangz", "headline": "", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "677218980", "reply_comment_id": "677088867", "reply_root_comment_id": "677086887", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "非杠啊！不做阅读理解的吗，我说了让你用临牌去浪、去违法操作吗？我的意思难道不是说 有“珍惜临牌，临牌期间违规是不扣分的”的(放松)想法 不妥，不管是处于什么阶段，上路了就是要有主动遵循交通规则的意识。", "like_count": 1, "author_name": "ehangz", "author_id": "5713a8d1d9bd7f18068ef5eb9d85604b", "author_is_anonymous": false}, {"url_token": "hong-tao-k-18-95", "headline": "自见者不明；自是者不彰；自伐者无功；自矜者不长。", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "677313501", "reply_comment_id": "677220665", "reply_root_comment_id": "677086887", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "[捂脸]不能友好一点嘛？你看了其他回复看了我对他们的回复吗？“因为朋友说我傻逼才上牌了提车，临牌不扣分。结果原来临牌也一样能识别扣分，没有取证就做答，这个是我的不对<br>当然要遵守交通规则，我说新手练车要珍惜是因为新手容易出错，比如把握不好距离出现压线，开车这么危险的事情，当然都会遵守规则珍爱生命啊，这点毋庸置疑<br>另外，看你凌晨一点多回复，友情建议，熬夜伤身体，早点休息", "like_count": 0, "author_name": "红桃K", "author_id": "3a1853a27d43c25b61912b4cd1dbbcec", "author_is_anonymous": false}, {"url_token": "hong-tao-k-18-95", "headline": "自见者不明；自是者不彰；自伐者无功；自矜者不长。", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "677088867", "reply_comment_id": "677086887", "reply_root_comment_id": "677086887", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "能不杠吗？不做阅读理解的吗，我说了让你用临牌去浪、去违法操作吗？我的意思难道不是新手练车难免出现状况外的情况，能减少点冲突咱们就减少吗", "like_count": 0, "author_name": "红桃K", "author_id": "3a1853a27d43c25b61912b4cd1dbbcec", "author_is_anonymous": false}]}, {"url_token": "hui-wen-he-28", "headline": "", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "686819489", "reply_comment_id": "0", "reply_root_comment_id": "686819489", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "除非你的车没有优惠，不然金融服务费是省不了的。主要利润就在这里。服务费给你免了，车价的优惠也就少了", "like_count": 1, "author_name": "惠文贺", "author_id": "1d389e25f86d1d824d4bb40f008d2068", "author_is_anonymous": false, "child_comment": [{"url_token": "hong-tao-k-18-95", "headline": "自见者不明；自是者不彰；自伐者无功；自矜者不长。", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "686983237", "reply_comment_id": "686819489", "reply_root_comment_id": "686819489", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "嗯嗯，大多数4s是这样综合优惠，所以要列出来对比", "like_count": 0, "author_name": "红桃K", "author_id": "3a1853a27d43c25b61912b4cd1dbbcec", "author_is_anonymous": false}]}, {"url_token": "dc1996-85", "headline": "", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "684357690", "reply_comment_id": "0", "reply_root_comment_id": "684357690", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "没有金融服务费只是4s店没说吧。它合并到车价里了给你少优惠个几千块", "like_count": 1, "author_name": "dc1996", "author_id": "b752660c8c1f43aca1df63b75028c5db", "author_is_anonymous": false, "child_comment": [{"url_token": "dc1996-85", "headline": "", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "684443744", "reply_comment_id": "684360097", "reply_root_comment_id": "684357690", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "这我同意。但我就是接触了好多我才会跟你说。所谓不收金融服务费的基本都是在车价里找回来了。免息贷款本质是厂家和4s店承担起了其中的费用，大部分4s店都不会去承担这一部分利息想着花样儿找回来。当然除非快倒闭以及某些品牌太难卖的，真的可能自己承担了。毕竟卖出去一辆是一辆", "like_count": 1, "author_name": "dc1996", "author_id": "b752660c8c1f43aca1df63b75028c5db", "author_is_anonymous": false}, {"url_token": "hong-tao-k-18-95", "headline": "自见者不明；自是者不彰；自伐者无功；自矜者不长。", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "684465285", "reply_comment_id": 